<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 shén de guó shù lì qǐ lái, shù lì qǐ lái, wàn guó de mín dōu xiàng tā jìng bài.
 tā de mín rú tiān shàng de xīng, hǎi biān de shā, biàn mǎn de miàn biàn mǎn de miàn.
 wǒ men de shén shì tiān xià de yé hé huá, wàn yǒu dōu běn yú tā,
 sì miàn bā fāng xiǎng qǐ, sòng zhǔ de gē shēng, gāo chàng hā lì lù yà!</lyrics>
<title>shén de guó 迦南72</title>
<hymn_number>72</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>